profile_positions.description:
I spent 2 months with Promaton working on their AI infrastructure to help setup a Project Lifecycle where they could keep track of Model Training, Testing and Serving.

In a short period of time we got the following in place:

* Jupyter Hub, with Github Single Sign On, deployed on K8S and with CPU and GPU flavours;
* MLflow, for experiment tracking, also on K8S;
* CI/CD, for model testing and TensorFlow Serving image creation, with GitHub and Jenkins.
